      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards of automotive preservation. This unit exhibits a flawless exterior finish and a showroom-quality interior, reflecting meticulous care and minimal usage. Mechanically superior and aesthetically pristine, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking a factory-standard driving experience. Inspection will confirm its unrivaled condition.",
